message: TOKEN2049 is an annual global conference where decision-makers in the crypto ecosystem connect to exchange ideas, network, and shape the industry.  The two-day event is a platform where the world's most influential figures, and organizations come together to build their network, hone their skills through workshops, and uncover learning opportunities. Besides the insightful panel discussions and keynotes, participants can also take part in a number of side activities like hackathons and parties.
